title: Did Mueller Conclude Trump Committed ‘No Obstruction’ in the 2016 Election Probe?
subtitle: Special Counsel Robert Mueller testified before Congress in July 2019 about his report on whether the Russian government interfered in the U.S. presidential election that Donald Trump won.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: U.S. President Donald Trump is correct to say that Special Counsel Robert Mueller's report on Russian interference in the U.S. 2016 presidential election found "no obstruction of justice."
